_sText: Aim_ag_tyr2 ----------- 12 players or less (preferred) Description: My second skill map. It is set within a small arena with objects placed tactically forcing you to use skill to eliminate your enemies. This is a texture map. It is a 2x2 checkerboard layout and works very well :) I made this map to my own design. Objective: Use the objects and environment to beat your enemies in gunfights. Pure skill will save you from getting that one headshot you didn't deserve...
